1
00:00:10,666 --> 00:00:12,000
[CREW A]
Destination sighted, sir,

2
00:00:12,083 --> 00:00:13,750
roughly thirty meters ahead.

3
00:00:13,833 --> 00:00:15,333
[CREW B]
Flood torpedo tube three.

4
00:00:15,416 --> 00:00:17,166
Bring her up as
steep as you can.

5
00:00:17,250 --> 00:00:18,916
Blow the ballast as well.

6
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:20,375
[CREW A] We'll be
making an emergency

7
